dcterms:creator: M. Kaya
et al.
dcterms:description: EEG dataset comprising recordings from 12 healthy participants, acquired using the EEG-1200 JE-921A system with a sampling frequency of 200 Hz. The dataset includes six-class motor imagery tasks: left-hand, right-hand, left-foot, right-foot, tongue, and rest tasks.
dcterms:title: EEG dataset presented by Kaya et al.

dcterms:creator: M. Tangermann
et al.
dcterms:description: BCI Competition dataset consisting of EEG data acquired from nine healthy participants using 22 Ag/AgCl EEG channels. The dataset includes four-class motor imagery tasks: left-hand, right-hand, left-foot, and right-foot movements.
dcterms:title: BCI Competition dataset
